00:22:45.350 --> 00:22:46.440
I'm all in.

00:22:46.440 --> 00:22:50.524
But I think what's also
helped me is that I'm tall.

00:22:50.524 --> 00:22:51.690
HILLARY BERGH: Yes, I agree.

00:22:51.690 --> 00:22:52.050
CARLA HALL: Right?

00:22:52.050 --> 00:22:53.050
