I'm here to stay.

00:23:23.650 --> 00:23:25.510
And I knew that I
could work long hours.

00:23:25.510 --> 00:23:27.400
I know that I'm strong.

00:23:27.400 --> 00:23:32.190
Physically strong, as well
as just emotionally strong.

00:23:32.190 --> 00:23:35.030
So I think determination
has a lot to do with it.

00:23:35.030 --> 00:23:37.620
And just basically digging
your heels in and saying,

00:23:37.620 --> 00:23:40.460
I'm here to stay.

00:23:40.460 --> 00:23:42.542
And I think, as women,
we apologize a lot

00:23:42.542 --> 00:23:43.750
because we're very nurturing.

00:23:43.750 --> 00:23:46.490
So we want everyone else
