You can do that as an option.

00:38:19.570 --> 00:38:21.080
If you really want
to get into it

00:38:21.080 --> 00:38:23.371
and you don't want to do the
whole certificate program,

00:38:23.371 --> 00:38:25.450
sometimes there are
evening programs,

00:38:25.450 --> 00:38:28.020
where there are about
six to eight weeks

00:38:28.020 --> 00:38:30.222
where you get the basics.

00:38:30.222 --> 00:38:33.520
And let me just be clear, going
to culinary school is great.

00:38:33.520 --> 00:38:36.390
It gives you the technique.

00:38:36.390 --> 00:38:39.130
