00:39:03.180 --> 00:39:03.670
CARLA HALL: Right.

00:39:03.670 --> 00:39:04.890
So you just wanted
that piece of paper

00:39:04.890 --> 00:39:06.450
to say that, I did something.

00:39:06.450 --> 00:39:09.570
And also, you were
18, so you probably

00:39:09.570 --> 00:39:11.830
wanted to have an experience
of going to school.

00:39:11.830 --> 00:39:12.830
HILLARY BERGH: Yes.

00:39:12.830 --> 00:39:14.340
CARLA HALL: As a
career changer, I

