went because I
needed a jump start.

00:39:16.020 --> 00:39:21.290
But for you, I would maybe
take that abbreviated course

00:39:21.290 --> 00:39:25.182
where you get technique,
and then you just play.

00:39:25.182 --> 00:39:27.680
And then you take
one-off classes

00:39:27.680 --> 00:39:29.450
and play and cook
for your friends.

00:39:29.450 --> 00:39:32.370
When I went to culinary
school, I actually

00:39:32.370 --> 00:39:35.540
would get my friends
to buy the ingredients

00:39:35.540 --> 00:39:36.910
and I would go and cook.

00:39:36.910 --> 00:39:38.254
Whatever turned out, turned out.

00:39:38.254 --> 00:39:40.670
If it was bad, I'm like, hey,
I don't know what I'm doing.

00:39:44.659 --> 00:39:45.700
There's always a way out.

00:39:45.700 --> 00:39:48.220
You always look
for that door out.

00:39:48.220 --> 00:39:50.162
Did I see another
person over here?

