00:40:02.790 --> 00:40:06.510
What does it take to be really
successful on that show other

00:40:06.510 --> 00:40:08.931
than cooking skills?

00:40:08.931 --> 00:40:10.930
CARLA HALL: Yes, well,
there are about 90 people

00:40:10.930 --> 00:40:11.860
working on the show.

00:40:11.860 --> 00:40:15.150
We have really
amazing producers.

00:40:15.150 --> 00:40:21.420
And the producers, we have
the executive producers,

00:40:21.420 --> 00:40:24.610
but we also have the people
who put the topics together.

