00:51:25.724 --> 00:51:27.140
CARLA HALL: Is
there a difference?

00:51:27.140 --> 00:51:32.709
Basically what the threads, and
where you are in the world--

00:51:32.709 --> 00:51:34.750
HILLARY BERGH: I don't
