00:51:39.430 --> 00:51:41.370
one plant in one
area of the world

00:51:41.370 --> 00:51:43.620
is going to be a little bit
different in another area

00:51:43.620 --> 00:51:45.940
of the world, even if
they're the exact same plant.

00:51:45.940 --> 00:51:47.640
CARLA HALL: Right
because of the soil.

00:51:47.640 --> 00:51:48.580
HILLARY BERGH: The
soil and things

00:51:48.580 --> 00:51:50.410
will have an influence
so, I'm sure there

00:51:50.410 --> 00:51:51.675
