HILLARY BERGH: Yeah.

00:53:05.670 --> 00:53:06.590
HILLARY BERGH: Room temperature.

00:53:06.590 --> 00:53:06.750
CARLA HALL: Room temperature.

00:53:06.750 --> 00:53:07.540
Not hot.

00:53:07.540 --> 00:53:08.800
HILLARY BERGH: Not hot.

00:53:08.800 --> 00:53:12.390
