personality, was that you

00:53:46.550 --> 00:53:48.022
had quite a few
vegetarian dishes.

00:53:48.022 --> 00:53:49.480
And I see in the
cookbook, you also

00:53:49.480 --> 00:53:52.040
have a non-meat section,
which as a vegetarian,

00:53:52.040 --> 00:53:53.470
I appreciate quite a bit.

00:53:53.470 --> 00:53:54.450
But it's unusual.

00:53:54.450 --> 00:53:57.280
A lot of chefs focus
