tah-dah effect

00:53:59.010 --> 00:54:00.350
if you have meat in dishes.

00:54:00.350 --> 00:54:04.940
I wonder is it just kind
of a natural inclination?

00:54:04.940 --> 00:54:06.860
Do you make a conscious
choice to incorporate

00:54:06.860 --> 00:54:08.165
