00:54:11.509 --> 00:54:12.800
HILLARY BERGH: I get that, too.

00:54:12.800 --> 00:54:15.560
CARLA HALL: Yeah,
you get that, too?

00:54:15.560 --> 00:54:18.970
Two reasons-- one, I love
vegetables, it's my favorite.

00:54:18.970 --> 00:54:21.220
I love vegetables.

00:54:21.220 --> 00:54:25.060
The other reason, on "Top Chef,"
was because as a caterer--

00:54:25.060 --> 00:54:27.290
and I was a caterer when
I went on "Top Chef."

00:54:27.290 --> 00:54:28.990
Now I'm a recovering caterer.

00:54:28.990 --> 00:54:33.630
It's been 925 days
since my last job.

00:54:33.630 --> 00:54:38.190
This is when you guys say,
hi, Carla, keep coming back.

00:54:38.190 --> 00:54:40.120
I would look at the menu.

00:54:40.120 --> 00:54:42.190
So a lot of times,
we would be doing

00:54:42.190 --> 00:54:45.330
an event where all
the food that we made

00:54:45.330 --> 00:54:48.320
was the only food that the
people who came to the event

00:54:48.320 --> 00:54:49.240
could have.

00:54:49.240 --> 00:54:52.640
So I would look at everything
that people were preparing

00:54:52.640 --> 00:54:55.360
and there wouldn't be
anything for the vegetarian.

00:54:55.360 --> 00:54:58.120
And I'm like, well what is
the vegetarian going to eat?

00:54:58.120 --> 00:54:59.290
This is what I'm thinking.

00:54:59.290 --> 00:55:01.670
What are they going to eat?

00:55:01.670 --> 00:55:05.020
Because I don't drink, I'm
always wanting the person

00:55:05.020 --> 00:55:09.790
with the specialty
food request to feel

00:55:09.790 --> 00:55:11.580
like, I thought about you.

00:55:11.580 --> 00:55:14.420
And that's why I did a
lot of vegetarian foods.

00:55:14.420 --> 00:55:17.860
And now I think it's much
easier to get vegetarian.

00:55:17.860 --> 00:55:21.500
But whenever I was
catering, I said

00:55:21.500 --> 00:55:23.182
please, if there
are any vegetarians,

00:55:23.182 --> 00:55:25.140
let me know ahead of time
because I didn't want

00:55:25.140 --> 00:55:27.270
