not cook that vegetable

00:55:32.880 --> 00:55:35.000
with some chicken stock.

00:55:35.000 --> 00:55:38.060
I mean that.

00:55:38.060 --> 00:55:42.546
My sense of catering to people
and wanting them to feel like I

00:55:42.546 --> 00:55:43.295
thought about you.

00:55:43.295 --> 00:55:44.350
I knew you were coming.

00:55:44.350 --> 00:55:47.420
So here have this dish.

00:55:47.420 --> 00:55:50.790
And also my love for vegetables.

